Company Overview of Verus Financial Partners, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Verus Financial Partners, Inc. provides financial planning, taxes, and investments services for personal needs. The company was formerly known as Kuehl Shepherd Kozlowski and Associates, Inc. and changed its name to Verus Financial Partners, Inc. in April 2012. Verus Financial Partners, Inc. was founded in 1992 and is based in Richmond, Virginia.


